message.body: Hey Gabbi, what was your schedule issue? I remember you saying you had to come in one day for only one class
I switched out of the Friday ensemble, so thats not the case anymore
Ok. My schedule has gotten a little thrown about. Are Mondays at all an option for you? If not, we can stick with what we've got.
Wednesdays are much better for me, my only option on Monday would be at 10
